{"tid":1934380,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[情緒病] 開多次，有無人陪打舊 Game 流星牛肉刀？ (45mb 免安裝版)","createTime":"2020-03-20T02:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T16:52:05.000Z","uid":252975,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"293c4832d2d93a9925d026251282ce2c0a9cfec9","tid":1934380,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唉，心情好差，要好好放鬆一下，驚下一個出事係我 (利申唔係股票)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVDuzXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVDuzXm.jpg&h=1e16bf35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Pe9zXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Pe9zXm.jpg&h=f39884a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎玩過同未玩過嘅朋友，一齊享受武俠打鬥快感，遊戲 N 年歷史，網絡格鬥遊戲神作<br />\n<br />\n45mb 精簡版，免安裝解壓即玩得！<br />\n<br />\n遊戲下載網址: <a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!Ml8k3axK!xOSTCpiHxpcaNrrAHfHHTA3ZKDPbxCx7PSmmE5H05r0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21Ml8k3axK%21xOSTCpiHxpcaNrrAHfHHTA3ZKDPbxCx7PSmmE5H05r0&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=9df5e3ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!Ml8k3axK!xOSTCpiHxpcaNrrAHfHHTA3ZKDPbxCx7PSmmE5H05r0</a><br />\n<br />\n注意提示: 舊遊戲破解版，防毒軟體容易報錯，自行決定安裝解壓與否。<br />\n<br />\n解壓後按次序點擊 註冊遊戲路徑.reg &gt; config.exe 設定不要全畫面 開啟遊戲 &gt; 流星直連器.exe<br />\n<br />\n直連器輸入 IP <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「61.244.153.166」</span></span>並確認回到遊戲，去區域網絡就會見到場~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">遊戲出招表 <a href=\"https://wiki2.gamer.com.tw/wiki.php?n=4516:%E6%8B%9B%E5%BC%8F%E8%A1%A8&amp;ss=4516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki2.gamer.com.tw%2Fwiki.php%3Fn%3D4516%3A%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BC%258F%25E8%25A1%25A8%26ss%3D4516&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=c2dd1738\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki2.gamer.com.tw/wiki.php?n=4516:%E6%8B%9B%E5%BC%8F%E8%A1%A8&amp;ss=4516</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">常見問題:<br />\n1) Windows 10 進遊戲亂碼，去控制台設置 非 Unicode 做返繁體中文 (香港)<br />\n詳細可以瀏覽 <a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3286189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3286189&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=df0af420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3286189</a><br />\n2) Windows 10 打開遊戲無反應，請將解壓資料夾放到 Program File，再點擊1.註冊遊戲路徑.reg 再嘗試</span></div>"},{"pid":"21a7906e142cc291fd43a98cbbe74e557aa0435d","tid":1934380,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多人要開工開學咩，定已經無人有 pc..."},{"pid":"80e3472f6b4bd2e576e02c14bdbf10b0ee6f5059","tid":1934380,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58093306fc23d6703b6b4e7b4dc86e07aa9c175e","tid":1934380,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登仔一個人能打都未有... 太令我失望喇"},{"pid":"09a8421bdf16263f0fde9c2220147c70e5c1d8c0","tid":1934380,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf1d268be94e3e1e1383d7541c8bdd7cb78a206","tid":1934380,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09a8421bdf16263f0fde9c2220147c70e5c1d8c0","tid":1934380,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"夠擔入嚟，打很死您 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hk